headline: Citigroup Maintains Buy on Arch Capital Group, Raises Price Target to $120
summary: Citigroup  analyst Matthew Heimermann   maintains Arch Capital Group (NASDAQ:ACGL) with a Buy and raises the price target from $113 to $120.

headline: Keefe, Bruyette & Woods Maintains Market Perform on Arch Capital Group, Raises Price Target to $104
summary: Keefe, Bruyette & Woods  analyst Meyer Shields   maintains Arch Capital Group (NASDAQ:ACGL) with a Market Perform and raises the price target from $102 to $104.
